GOAL: Set map intent to show a marker 
SOLUTION: Add "?q=" + coordinates to Uri.parse
- Intent map = new Intent(Intent.ACTION_VIEW, Uri.parse("geo:" + coordinates + "?q=" + coordinates))
ADD-ON: Include label name on map intent by adding "+ '(' + location_name + ')'" to Uri.parse()
- Intent map = new Intent(Intent.ACTION_VIEW, Uri.parse("geo:" + coordinates + "?q=" + coordinates + "(" + label + ")"))

